SELECT `buyers`.`id`, `buyer_name`, `buyer_details`.`cc` as `cc`, SUM(buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_qty, SUM(buy_cost) as buy_cost, SUM(buy_cost * buyer_details.buyer_qty) as total_buy_cost FROM `buyer_details` JOIN `buyers` ON `buyers`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`buyer` JOIN `purchase_items` ON `purchase_items`.`id` = `buyer_details`.`purchase_id` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE `purchase_items`.`created_at` >= '2024-02-01 00:00:00' AND `purchase_items`.`created_at` <= '2024-02-22 23:59:59' AND `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '26' GROUP BY `buyer_details`.`cc`

SELECT YEAR(purchase_items.created_at) as year, MONTHNAME(purchase_items.created_at) as month, SUM(purchase_items.qty) as qty, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.buy_cost) as buy_cost, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.market_price) as sell_price, SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.profit) as profit, ((SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.profit) / SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.market_price))*0.6) * 100 as margin, ((SUM(purchase_items.qty* lead_lists.profit) / SUM(purchase_items.qty * lead_lists.buy_cost))*100) as roi FROM `purchase_items` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE YEAR(purchase_items.created_at) = YEAR(NOW()) AND `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '26' GROUP BY YEAR(purchase_items.created_at), MONTH(purchase_items.created_at)

SELECT `lead_lists`.`title`, `lead_lists`.`asin`, `orders_status`.`purchased_date`, `purchase_items`.`qty`, SUM(qty_received) as total_received, ABS((SUM(IFNULL(qty_returned, 0)))) as total_refund, ABS((SUM(qty_received + IFNULL(qty_returned, 0))) - (purchase_items.qty)) as total_unreceived FROM `orders_status` JOIN `purchase_items` ON `purchase_items`.`id` = `orders_status`.`purchased_item_id` JOIN `lead_lists` ON `lead_lists`.`id` = `purchase_items`.`lead_id` WHERE `lead_lists`.`file_id` = '26' AND DATE(purchase_items.created_at) >= '2024-02-01' AND DATE(purchase_items.created_at) <= '2024-02-22' GROUP BY `lead_lists`.`id` ORDER BY `purchase_items`.`id` DESC
